UID:wCibApIUB8FdcgAH6vuEyquAv-sodalponte@gmail.com
ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;X-NUM-GUE
 STS=0:mailto:sodalponte@gmail.com
URL:https://hopin.com/magic_links/1ce2467f-e849-4653-912d-3bdf9e75078d/acce
 pt
CLASS:CONFIDENTIAL
CREATED:20220323T084326Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>You're invited to <i>WomenHack Barcelona (virtual)</i>\, an 
 online invite-only networking and recruiting event focused on women in tech
 nology: <strong>developers\, UX/UI designers\, data folks\, and product man
 agers.&nbsp\;</strong></p><figure class="image"><img src="https://cdn.evbuc
 .com/eventlogos/226347176/womenhackimagenewoneresized.jpg"></figure><p><br>
 Whether you are actively looking for your next challenge\, curious about ot
 her opportunities in your area\, or just interested in networking with othe
 r companies and individuals who support gender diversity – <i><strong>join 
 us for a fun and engaging evening!</strong></i><br><br><i><strong>** We sug
 gest using the latest version of Chrome (web browser) for this event.</stro
 ng></i></p><p><br><strong>MEET TOP LOCAL COMPANIES</strong><br>WomenHack gi
 ves you 1:1 meetings with industry players in your city. Events are organiz
 ed in a rapid chats format (5-min each) to keep things engaging and include
  a happy hour where you can network and meet fellow women in tech.<br>&nbsp
 \;</p><p><strong>WHY ATTEND WOMENHACK EVENTS?</strong><br>Get an insider’s 
 perspective on the various interesting technologies and projects that compa
 nies are working on\, learn about companies’ benefits and team culture firs
 thand\, and the opportunity to meet each team's key players such as develop
 ers\, managers\, and even C-levels face-to-face.&nbsp\;</p><p><br><strong>W
 HAT YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT WOMENHACK EVENTS:</strong></p><p>– <strong>What 
 if my employer is there?</strong><br>Don’t worry\, we will send out the lis
 t of companies attending prior to the event. Our team also screens through 
 each attendee to make sure there is no conflict of interest. Your employer 
 will never be informed that you have signed up for this event. When you app
 ly\, please make sure to mention your current employer’s on the signup form
 .</p><p>– <strong>Do I have to be looking for a new job?</strong><br>While 
 you don’t necessarily have to be actively looking for a new job\, we’d like
  you to know that our event revolves around recruiting. It is an opportunit
 y for both passive and active job seekers to explore what the market has to
  offer\, speak with recruiting teams in a casual setting\, and learn more a
 bout companies’ diversity and promotion policies.</p><p>&nbsp\;– <strong>I’
 m not a woman\, can I still attend?</strong><br>Absolutely\, our events are
  designed to promote gender diversity in the workplace and anyone who belie
 ves in this mission can attend!</p><p>– <strong>Why was I invited?</strong>
 <br>To ensure the quality of our events\, we are currently invite-only. If 
 you received an invite\, you were probably on our waitlist or were invited 
 by someone on our talent ops team who thinks you might be a good fit for th
 e companies looking to hire.</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://cdn
 .evbuc.com/eventlogos/226347176/womenhackead2019resized.jpg"></figure><p><b
 r><br>*<i>WomenHack promotes gender diversity in the workplace but all are 
 welcome to attend our events. If you have any questions regarding our polic
 ies\, </i><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://womenh
 ack.com/contact/"><i>contact us here</i></a><i>.</i></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220323T084942Z
LOCATION:https://hopin.com/magic_links/1ce2467f-e849-4653-912d-3bdf9e75078d
 /accept
SEQUENCE:1648025006
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:WomenHack Barcelona - March 2022
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
