UID:7ci1cq7tboie3i2nj7d7bahk8f@google.com
CREATED:20240419T104749Z
DESCRIPTION:The rise of AI has undoubtedly raised concerns about student as
 sessment\, cheating\, and ethical considerations amongst Business Schools. 
 Is GenAI an ultimate threat to higher education? Are there opportunities to
  GenAI in students learning? Can we rethink assessment in the presence of G
 enAI? \n\nThese are questions educators like yourself have been asking sinc
 e the advent of ChatGPT early in November 2023 and that we will raise in ou
 r Panel Discussion this April 25th at 3:30 p.m CEST. Join our top-tier pane
 lists from HEC\, ESSEC & EDHEC and panel facilitator Dan Hasan from Feedbac
 kFruits to learn about success stories and gain practical insights.
LAST-MODIFIED:20240419T104749Z
LOCATION:https://eu01web.zoom.us/j/69599167664
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Webinar: Generative AI in Higher Ed: Rethinking Learning strategies
  for French Business Schools
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
