 STS=0:mailto:sodalponte@gmail.com
CREATED:20240619T152303Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Are you ready to elevate your design game and embrace a more
  adaptive\, flexible approach? Figma variables are no longer exclusive to d
 evelopers—they're a game-changer for designers too! 🌟 Embrace this superpo
 wer and create exceptional\, user-centric designs!</p><p>What you’ll get ou
 t of this course:</p><ul><li><strong>Use color variables like a pro</strong
 >Build color palettes that differentiate between primitive color values\, s
 emantic colors\, and component-specific colors.</li><li><strong>Use numbers
  to define spacing and sizing systems</strong>Stop pixel-pushing and start 
 using a system that translates more immediately to the implementation of yo
 ur designs.</li><li><strong>Integrate variables into a system of typography
  styles</strong>Make your typography styles more powerful using variables t
 o support responsive design.</li><li><strong>Communicate better with develo
 pers</strong>Your developers already think in terms of variables and condit
 ional logic. Now you can too without leaving the comfort of Figma!</li><li>
 </li></ul><p>📅 Course Details:</p><ul><li>Total Duration:8 hours (4 sessio
 ns of 2 hours each)</li><li>Dates: July 22\, 24\, 29\, &amp\; 31</li><li>Ti
 mings: Pacific: 9:30am – 11:30am // Eastern: 12:30pm – 2:30pm // CET: 6:30p
 m – 8:30pm</li></ul><p>Join the course here: <a href="https://maven.com/but
 ton-school/figma-variables">https://maven.com/button-school/figma-variables
 </a></p><p>Don't miss out on this opportunity to transform your design work
 flow and bring more consistency and creativity into your work. Secure your 
 spot now and level up your design skills! 🔥</p><p>#FigmaVariables #DesignC
 ourse #UserExperience #AdaptiveDesign DesignersUnite #ConFig2024 #Figma #UX
 UI #UIDesign #DesignSystems DesignTokens</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260404T115144Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Second Button School Linkedin Post
TRANSP:OPAQUE
