DESCRIPTION:<p>Hey Ironhacker!<br><br>Happy New Year to you all! </p><p>I h
 ope you are as excited as we are about the start of your Bootcamp! </p><p>O
 n our side\, we have been preparing everything for your start. For that\, w
 e will be hosting the Day 0 session on <b>Thursday 4th of January at 18:00 
 CET</b>. </p><p>In this session we will chat about what to expect and what 
 to have ready by the beginning of the course and you can ask any questions 
 you might have. </p><p><b>We highly encourage you to join</b>\, but this se
 ssion won't be mandatory.</p><p>Hope to see you there 🚀</p>\n\n-::~:~::~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::
